A group of people who are allowed to see the ugly part of me , that I keep hidden , even from those closest to me , because they don ' t judge , but help me in anyway they can . And even though I am no longer able to update for my favourite shows , I still visit the Forums daily , checking up on the latest news , updates and on my friends , because this has become my favourite place in cyberspace . Love , Radz Posted in : Cafe Chit Chat with Dilbagh ( DramaholicVibes ) Posted on : 28 October 2009 at 12 : 00am